{"tid":261233,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"清真咖哩","createTime":"2017-05-28T09:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T09:59:21.000Z","uid":62277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e98554e06a8611923949ea15f5ca65a19424f74b","tid":261233,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"食咖哩好睇個人口味<br />\n有人鍾意港式、馬拉咖哩<br />\n接受唔到重口味既印度咖哩<br />\n<br />\n我個人就鍾意更重口味既巴基斯坦、清真咖哩<br />\n嗰種辣椒香、薑味好正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咖哩羊腩<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/174601_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F174601_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d835922a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賣相無其他咖哩咁好,但更濃<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/174746_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F174746_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=83a6840e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無印度咖哩咁杰身,其實淋少少上飯已好夠味<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/174919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F174919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0f72f173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/174955_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F174955_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ddc33a02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7f07545be0e69cbf5428d280f1a4ab616c74868","tid":261233,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"係邊度同幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62684b03f61fbde